Bassa proxy
===========
* Fixing bugs related to Content-Length of file being sent (basically a mismatch between actual size of the file and the size said by Content-Length)
* Implementing Configuration module
* Proxy module API
* Module for communicating with Bassa content sharing system (Bassa_svr)
* Implementing a Google search intercepting module and integrating it with Bassa content sharer's content search engine

Bassa server (Content sharer)
=============================
* Implementing module API
* Rewriting modules developed for earlier version
* Implementing a content tagging service and search engine API
* Implementing content search engine

Bassa client
============
* Implementing bassa client web UI for listing content and downloading content with social networking aspects
